content.text: Good, the `schools` table has a `Phone` column and can be joined with `satscores` via `CDSCode`/`cds`. Now let me compute the top 3 SAT excellence rates and get their phone numbers.

input.command:
sqlite3 -header -column "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "
SELECT s.sname, s.NumGE1500, s.NumTstTakr, 
       CAST(s.NumGE1500 AS REAL) / s.NumTstTakr AS excellence_rate,
       sch.Phone
FROM satscores s
JOIN schools sch ON s.cds = sch.CDSCode
WHERE s.NumTstTakr > 0 AND s.NumGE1500 IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY excellence_rate DESC
LIMIT 5;
"
input.description: Get top 5 schools by SAT excellence rate with phone numbers
